<p><a href="https://echarts.apache.org/handbook/zh/concepts/style" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">官网 - theme 主题<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>
<a href="https://echarts.apache.org/zh/theme-builder.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">主题编辑器<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// HTML 引入 vintage.js 文件后（假设主题名称是 "vintage"）</span>
