<span class="token comment">// ...</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br></div></div><p><strong>svg 渲染</strong> - 设置 renderer 参数 为 'canvas' 或 'svg' 即可指定渲染器(默认 Canvas)</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> chart <span class="token operator">=</span> echarts<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">init</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>dom<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'主题名称'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token literal-property property">renderer</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">'svg'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div></template>
